# All the adpositions
PATTERNS
TruePreposition
TruePrepositionVary
TruePostposition
TruePostpositionVary
DerivedPostposition
DerivedPostpositionVary
FrozenPreposition
FrozenPrepositionVary
FrozenPostposition
FrozenPostpositionVary

#Declinable postpositions are computed in the nouns paradigm file



